Welcome to "fy_deagle_western_03"

Map created By El_Mexicano


This is an "FY" map , with 12 slots in each team, 12 slots for the terrorists & 12 
slots for the counter-terroristes!
Which means that there is no aim , the only aim is to kill all players of the other team!
It's a "FUN" map , that's why all the creation of this map was based on the FUN side 
of the map trying to do a "western " atmosphere !

The .BSP file makes 3,7 MO, the .NAV file makes 150 ko 

Big thanks to the LoS*LaTiNoS production for their help & all the team for the help they gave me
